tbl_npc.target_text_3: We are proud of our armors, which are the best....

tbl_npc.name: Rosay David Hall (Glove)
tbl_npc.target_text_1: Are you still hesitating? We are about to close... Please hurry up!
tbl_npc.target_text_2: It's a little expensive but the best in performance.
tbl_npc.target_text_3: Nowadays, people just look around.. They don't buy...

tbl_npc.name: Elizabeth Greensberg (Boots)
tbl_npc.target_text_1: I never sell belongings of the war dead. Please trust me!
tbl_npc.target_text_2: It's a little expensive but the best in performance.
tbl_npc.target_text_3: We are proud of our armors, which are the best....

tbl_npc.name: Eric Szmander (Grocer)
tbl_npc.target_text_1: Welcome!
tbl_npc.target_text_2: How can I help you?
tbl_npc.target_text_3: Clearly, performance is commensurate with price...

tbl_npc.name: Philip Conserba (Weapon Sheet)
tbl_npc.target_text_1: Do you want to manufacture weapons? You found the right place!
tbl_npc.target_text_2: This must not be regarded as expensive!
tbl_npc.target_text_3: I can't guarantee success..

tbl_npc.name: James C. Hatt (Mail Sheet)
tbl_npc.target_text_1: Mr. Philip is selling weapon sheets, next door to me. Please look around and see armor sheets here!
tbl_npc.target_text_2: This must not be regarded as expensive!
tbl_npc.target_text_3: Even though it fails... no refund...

tbl_npc.name: Anthony Zuiker (Armor Sheet)
tbl_npc.target_text_1: The best choice is to make and wear it for yourself.
tbl_npc.target_text_2: This must not be regarded as expensive!
tbl_npc.target_text_3: Using it makes you see the performance.

tbl_npc.name: Josh Birman (Magic Sheet)
tbl_npc.target_text_1: Are you looking for better weapons and armors?
tbl_npc.target_text_2: This must not be regarded as expensive!
tbl_npc.target_text_3: Reversal in life.. Your dream can be realized here.

tbl_npc.name: Jerry Stahl (Guild Manager)
tbl_npc.target_text_1: Oh! Are you trying to create your own guild?
tbl_npc.target_text_2: The guild is really an important organization.
tbl_npc.target_text_3: Only the registered guild is allowed.

tbl_npc.name: Lou Antonio (Merc. Manager)
tbl_npc.target_text_1: Mercenaries are waiting to swear allegiance to you!
tbl_npc.target_text_2: Knight mercenaries lure enemies out when the employer is in danger.
tbl_npc.target_text_3: Cleric mercenaries use healing and buff.

tbl_npc.target_text_1: People are working even in this place. I volunteered to come this far at the request of the knight group.
tbl_npc.target_text_2: I have yet to prepare all the items but you will be satisfied.
tbl_npc.target_text_3: If you want other items, please visit our village...

tbl_npc.target_text_2: My elder sister living in the capital is selling other gems.
tbl_npc.target_text_3: Why don't you buy it right now? If you want to smash even the armor of the enemy...

tbl_npc.name: Tobey Maguire (Wool)
tbl_npc.target_text_1: Now, I am selling wool....
tbl_npc.target_text_2: I have yet to find cashmere.
tbl_npc.target_text_3: The eye, eye, looking at me...

tbl_npc.name: Ebbot Bing (Banker)
tbl_npc.target_text_1: Welcome! How can I help you?
tbl_npc.target_text_2: I am in charge of storing items and exchanging cash.
tbl_npc.target_text_3: When you get your item back, you should pay storage.

tbl_npc.name: Geena Davis (Guild Cloak)
tbl_npc.target_text_1: I am selling guild capes.
tbl_npc.target_text_2: If you are a guild member, please wear a cape bearing the guild mark.
tbl_npc.target_text_3: The guild master designated the mark.

tbl_npc.name: Salt Village Guard
tbl_npc.target_text_1: Don't talk to me. I am working now!
tbl_npc.target_text_3: You may be...No! I mistook you for another person.

tbl_npc.target_text_1: The trip to the island is prohibited.... It's impossible!
tbl_npc.target_text_3: If you are a stranger...leave right now!
